I want to implement a License Blocker in this app.

Goal

Users must not be able to proceed or use any part of the app until they enter and activate a valid license key.

License Activation API

When the user submits a license key, call the following endpoint:

GET https://testfinder.io/wp-json/lmfwc/v2/licenses/activate/%7BLICENSE_KEY%7D


Authorization Header (Basic Auth):

Authorization: Basic Y2tfMzJlZGE3YzljM2E4NjUyYmVkMzVjOTRiMzM2MGY1ODczZjkyOWNkYzpjc184MDIzZDJlMzc1YzYxOTUxMGMwM2I1ODFiMjdmMjRhZjkyOTFlM2Zi

Expected API Responses
License Expired

If the license key is expired, the API responds with:

{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "errors": {
      "lmfwc_rest_license_expired": [
        "The license Key expired on 2026-01-18 00:00:00 (UTC)."
      ]
    },
    "error_data": {
      "lmfwc_rest_license_expired": {
        "status": 404
      }
    }
  }
}


Behavior:

Show an error message stating the license is expired

Do NOT allow access to the app

License Invalid

If the license key is invalid or not found:

{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "errors": {
      "lmfwc_rest_data_error": [
        "License Key: CFDA-54CD-C64F-52AS could not be found."
      ]
    },
    "error_data": {
      "lmfwc_rest_data_error": {
        "status": 404
      }
    }
  }
}


Behavior:

Show an error message stating the license is invalid

Do NOT allow access to the app

License Active

If the license key is valid and active:

{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "id": 1,
    "orderId": 6540,
    "productId": 6535,
    "userId": 0,
    "licenseKey": "1C26-66B1-CBDB-AE3F",
    "expiresAt": "2026-02-13 22:49:57",
    "validFor": 30,
    "source": 1,
    "status": 2,
    "timesActivated": 5,
    "timesActivatedMax": 1000,
    "createdAt": "2026-01-14 22:49:57",
    "createdBy": 1,
    "updatedAt": "2026-01-19 21:49:30",
    "updatedBy": 1,
    "activationData": {
      "id": 5,
      "token": "89e28ebff11b5c1541cfbc23a954124259104b7e",
      "license_id": 1,
      "source": 2,
      "ip_address": "86.29.249.101",
      "user_agent": "PostmanRuntime/7.51.0"
    }
  }
}


Behavior:

Mark the license as activated

Unlock full app functionality

Display the active license key at the top of the app UI

UI / UX Requirements (IMPORTANT)

Prompt the user for a license key immediately on first launch or import

The entire app must be blocked until a valid license is activated

Show the license input screen before any other UI

Once activated:

Display the license key at the top of the app

Enable all other features

License Key Format

The license key must match this format:

CFDA-54CD-C64F-52AD


(4 groups of 4 alphanumeric characters separated by hyphens)
